flags inject version/commit/build date\n378: - [ ] Unit tests for each binary's main entry point\n379: - [ ] `go test ./cmd/... -cover` >70% coverage\n380: - [ ] `go vet ./cmd/...` passes\n381: - [ ] `golangci-lint run ./cmd/...` passes\n382: - [ ] Package structure follows agentcube conventions\n383: \n384: ---\n385: \n386: ## File Changes Summary\n387: \n388: | File | Action | Lines Changed | Description |\n389: |------|--------|---------------|-------------|\n390: | `cmd/internal/cli/version.go` | Create | ~20 | Version constants and build info |\n391: | `cmd/internal/cli/flagset.go` | Create | ~30 | Common flag handling utilities |\n392: | `cmd/internal/cli/logging.go` | Create | ~20 | klog initialization helper |\n393: | `cmd/internal/cli/signal.go` | Create | ~25 | Signal handling for graceful shutdown |\n394: | `cmd/agentcube/main.go` | Create | ~80 | Main CLI binary entry point |\n395: | `cmd/agentcube/main_test.go` | Create | ~50 | Unit tests for agentcube CLI |\n396: | `cmd/agentd/main.go` | Create | ~100 | Agent daemon binary entry point |\n397: | `cmd/agentd/main_test.go` | Create | ~60 | Unit tests for agentd daemon |\n398: | `cmd/agentsandbox/main.go` | Create | ~60 | Sandbox runtime binary entry point |\n399: | `cmd/agentsandbox/main_test.go` | Create | ~40 | Unit tests for agentsandbox runtime |\n400: | `cmd/agentctl/main.go` | Create | ~120 | Control tool binary entry point |\n401: | `cmd/agentctl/main_test.go` | Create | ~80 | Unit tests for agentctl commands |\n402: | `Makefile` | Modify | +40 | Build targets for all binaries |\n403: | `build/Dockerfile.agentcube` | Create | ~25 | Multi-stage Docker build |\n404: | `build/Dockerfile.agentd` | Create | ~25 | Multi-stage Docker build |\n405: | `build/Dockerfile.agentsandbox` | Create | ~25 | Multi-stage Docker build |\n406: | `build/Dockerfile.agentctl` | Create | ~25 | Multi-stage Docker build |\n407: \n408: ---\n409: \n410: ## Implementation Notes\n411: \n412: - **Design completed at Stage ST-3**\n413: - **Reference implementation**: `cmd/picod/main.go` provides pattern for sandbox binary\n414: - **Common patterns**: All binaries use klog for logging, flag for CLI parsing\n415: - **Version injection**: Use ldflags at build time for dynamic version info\n416: - **Integration points**:\n417:   - `pkg/agentd` — IdleCleanupController for agentd\n418:   - `pkg/picod` — Server for agentsandbox runtime\n419:   - `pkg/router` — SessionManager for agentd/agentctl\n420:   - `pkg/workloadmanager` — K8sClient for agentd/agentctl\n421:   - `pkg/store` — Store interface for session state\n422:   - `pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1` — CRD types for agentctl\n423: - **Binary naming**:\n424:   - `agentcube`: Main CLI for agent lifecycle (pack/build/publish/invoke/status)\n425:   - `agentd`: Daemon for idle cleanup and session monitoring\n426:   - `agentsandbox`: Sandbox pod runtime sidecar\n427:   - `agentctl`: Admin control tool for K8s resource management\n428: - **Output format**: agentctl supports table, json, yaml formats\n429: - **Signal handling**: All binaries handle SIGTERM/SIGINT for Kubernetes compatibility\n430: \n431: ---\n432: \n433: ## Implementation Timeline\n434: \n435: | Phase | Tasks | Status | Completion |\n436: |-------|-------|--------|------------|\n437: | Phase 1: Shared CLI Infrastructure | T1.1, T1.2, T1.3, T1.4 | Pending | 0% |\n438: | Phase 2: agentcube CLI Binary | T2.1, T2.2, T2.3, T2.4 | Pending | 0% |\n439: | Phase 3: agentd Daemon Binary | T3.1, T3.2, T3.3, T3.4, T3.5 | Pending | 0% |\n440: | Phase 4: agentsandbox Runtime Binary | T4.1, T4.2, T4.3, T4.4, T4.5 | Pending | 0% |\n441: | Phase 5: agentctl Control Tool Binary | T5.1-T5.7 | Pending | 0% |\n442: | Phase 6: Build Configuration | T6.1, T6.2, T6.3, T6.4 | Pending | 0% |\n443: | Phase 7: Unit Tests | T7.1-T7.6 | Pending | 0% |\n444: | Phase 8: Integration & Validation | T8.1-T8.5 | Pending | 0% |\n445: \n446: **Total Progress: 0% Complete (0/35 tasks)**\n\n(End of file - total 446 lines)\n</co