{"type":"text","timestamp":1775868149143,"sessionID":"ses_286037c4dffe1uedSL24Jhd5aN","part":{"id":"prt_d79fd628f001JEv595LLDVItGd","messageID":"msg_d79fd3174001TkyQSGFFY4tGA4","sessionID":"ses_286037c4dffe1uedSL24Jhd5aN","type":"text","text":"Based on my analysis of AR-019:\n\n## Summary\n\n### Completed\n\n**Phase 1 (Shared CLI Infrastructure):**\n- `cmd/internal/cli/version.go` — Version constants, GitCommit, BuildDate, VersionInfo struct\n- `cmd/internal/cli/flagset.go` — FlagSet struct with Verbose/Kubeconfig/Namespace flags\n- `cmd/internal/cli/logging.go` — InitLogging() with klog initialization\n- `cmd/internal/cli/signal.go` — SetupSignalHandler() for SIGTERM/SIGINT graceful shutdown\n\n**Phase 2 (agentcube CLI):**\n- `cmd/agentcube/main.go` — Full implementation with subcommands: pack, build, publish, invoke, status (placeholder implementations)\n- Version/help flags functional\n\n**Phase 3 (agentd daemon):**\n- `cmd/agentd/main.go` — Integrates IdleCleanupController, K8sClient, LifecycleManager\n- Flags: idle-cleanup-interval, idle-timeout, kubeconfig, namespace\n\n### Deferred\n\n- **Phase 4**: `cmd/agentsandbox/main.go` — Empty directory, no implementation\n- **Phase 5**: `cmd/agentctl/main.go` — Empty directory, no implementation\n- **Phase 6**: Makefile build targets, Dockerfiles — Not created\n- **Phase 7**: Unit tests — No `*_test.go` files in cmd/\n- **Phase 8**: Integration/validation — **Build error**: unused `time` import in `cmd/agentd/main.go:8`\n\n**Progress**: ~30% (6 tasks from Phases 1-3 completed, remaining 29 tasks deferred)","time":{"start":1775868149140,"end":1775868149140}}}
